%N A393956 Expansion of e.g.f. (5*t/2) * (cos(t/2) - cos(3*t/2)) / sin(5*t/2) (even powers only).
%D A393956 A. Fletcher, J. C. P. Miller, L. Rosenhead and L. J. Comrie, An Index of Mathematical Tables. Vols. 1 and 2, 2nd ed., Blackwell, Oxford and Addison-Wesley, Reading, MA, 1962, Vol. 1, p. 77. The last given term has an error.
%p A393956 egf:= (5*t/2) * (cos(t/2) - cos(3*t/2)) / sin(5*t/2):
%p A393956 a:= n-> (2*n)!*coeff(series(egf, t, 2*n+3), t, 2*n):
%p A393956 seq(a(n), n=1..16);  # _Alois P. Heinz_, Mar 04 2026
%t A393956 n=10; (CoefficientList[(5t/2)(Cos[t/2]-Cos[3t/2])/Sin[5t/2]+O[t]^(2n+1),t] Range[0,2n]!)[[3;;;;2]]
%K A393956 nonn,easy,new
%O A393956 1,1
